08:46.070 --> 08:47.169
- Okay, go ahead.

08:47.169 --> 08:48.029
Pretend you didn't hear it.

08:48.029 --> 08:51.200
You know, sometimes
we are able

08:51.200 --> 08:55.830
to figure these things out
because we are lucky.

08:55.830 --> 08:57.370
Sometimes we're able
to figure them out

08:57.370 --> 08:58.929
