09:16.269 --> 09:18.529
because he's an idiot!

09:18.529 --> 09:22.070
Now if that mistake had been
on your shorts,

09:22.070 --> 09:25.399
you would've killed us
absolutely dead.

09:25.399 --> 09:27.929
If you had the X
that then has the O around it,

09:27.929 --> 09:29.200
it would've killed us dead.

09:29.200 --> 09:32.230
One of the wonderful principles
of magic

09:32.230 --> 09:35.500
is that once the trick is done,

09:35.500 --> 09:38.169
you think that's the only way
it could've gone.

09:38.169 --> 09:40.730
And what I love about
what you've done

09:40.730 --> 09:45.570
is you've taken something
where we have many fewer choices

09:45.570 --> 09:48.370
than we think and made
it look like the choices

09:48.370 --> 09:49.570
are almost infinite.

09:49.570 --> 09:51.870
And I love that a lot.

09:51.870 --> 09:55.000
And if we're wrong about that,

09:55.000 --> 09:59.169
you can tell us to just
sit on it and rotate.

09:59.169 --> 10:00.570
