to see me jacked up.

10:20.200 --> 10:21.830
- Okay.
So you didn't fool them.

10:21.830 --> 10:23.169
You might have
stalked them a little.

10:23.169 --> 10:24.399
But you're adorable.

10:24.399 --> 10:26.200
So is your puppy.
We love you.

10:26.200 --> 10:29.500
Thank you, Robert Ramirez.

10:29.500 --> 10:32.769
- Thank you.
I'll see you tomorrow.

