11:09.570 --> 11:10.899
- My name is Dominik.

11:10.899 --> 11:13.429
The magic that I do is set
in a fantasy world.

11:13.429 --> 11:15.000
It's very visual.

11:15.000 --> 11:16.399
People say it's like
real magic.

11:16.399 --> 11:17.500
They call it wizardry.

11:17.500 --> 11:19.000
I like that.

11:19.000 --> 11:20.570
My father worked
for Jim Henson,

11:20.570 --> 11:22.500
and I was very inspired
by that.

11:22.500 --> 11:24.500
He created fantasy worlds.

11:24.500 --> 11:26.230
The puppeteers are magicians.

11:26.230 --> 11:30.570
They create life out
of inanimate fabric and foam.

11:30.570 --> 11:32.330
Everything I perform
is my own creation,

11:32.330 --> 11:34.529
hand-built from scratch.

11:34.529 --> 11:36.070
There is a tremendous
satisfaction

11:36.070 --> 11:38.899
that comes from imagining
an illusion or a routine

11:38.899 --> 11:40.529
and bringing it to life.

11:40.529 --> 11:42.169
The illusion that I'm gonna do
for Penn and Teller

11:42.169 --> 11:43.730
is brand-new.

11:43.730 --> 11:46.070
Nobody has ever seen anything
like this.

11:46.070 --> 11:47.169
If something goes wrong
with it,

11:47.169 --> 11:49.000
there is nothing I can do.

11:49.000 --> 11:51.200
My hands are literally tied.

11:51.200 --> 11:55.000
[cheers and applause]

11:55.000 --> 11:57.929
- Our next performer
once described himself

11:57.929 --> 11:59.700
as a boy who didn't grow up.

11:59.700 --> 12:03.230
Which means, like me, he still
sleeps in footie pajamas.

12:03.230 --> 12:06.100
Please welcome Dominik.

12:06.100 --> 12:08.330
[cheers and applause]

12:08.330 --> 12:10.200
- Hello, I'm Dominik.

12:10.200 --> 12:12.429
I'm here with Nova and Andrew.

12:12.429 --> 12:15.070
