something spectacular.

12:15.070 --> 12:19.029
An escape that Houdini
didn't attempt.

12:19.029 --> 12:21.029
Because he's dead.

12:21.029 --> 12:22.600
10 pounds of sharpened steel,

12:22.600 --> 12:25.169
an old butcher's block.

12:25.169 --> 12:27.669
Imagine the horrors.

12:27.669 --> 12:30.000
All you vegans
and vegetarians,

12:30.000 --> 12:31.500
