12:31.500 --> 12:34.429
This apple...

12:34.429 --> 12:35.830
is halved.

12:35.830 --> 12:37.429
Anything that gets put there

12:37.429 --> 12:39.669
will meet
with the same consequences.

12:41.769 --> 12:44.830
In a minute, that's where
my hands will go.

12:44.830 --> 12:46.830
I'm gonna be handcuffed
and shackled

12:46.830 --> 12:48.730
to that butcher's block.

12:48.730 --> 12:52.730
That rope, well, we're gonna
set that rope on fire,

12:52.730 --> 12:54.929
