13:12.100 --> 13:13.769
- I do, but no second hand.

13:13.769 --> 13:14.899
- Oh, no second hand.

13:14.899 --> 13:16.070
- Yeah, so you may be
in big trouble.

13:16.070 --> 13:18.100
- Well, you know what?

13:18.100 --> 13:20.230
I'm a professional.
I know what I'm doing.

13:20.230 --> 13:21.730
May I borrow it?

13:21.730 --> 13:23.230
- Sure.
- That'd be great.

13:23.230 --> 13:26.070
- I've got to tell you,
