13:34.500 --> 13:37.000
- Well, I'm putting my hands
at risk

13:37.000 --> 13:38.169
for your entertainment.

13:38.169 --> 13:39.200
- Good thinking.

13:39.200 --> 13:40.700
- So now you've got some skin
